<div class="row">
	<div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
		<div class="page-header">
			<h1>Buy or extend membership</h1>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
	<div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
		{{{alert}}}
		<p>Your current membership expires on: {{expiration}}</p>
		<p>Six months of membership is currently ${{price}}</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
	<div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
		<h4>Payment method:</h4>
		<p>The following account will be billed with the membership fee:</p>
		<form class="form-signin" method="post">
        <div class="form-group">
        	<label for="membershipCardNumber">Credit or Debit Card Number</label>
        	<input type="text" class="form-control" id="membershipCardNumber" name="membershipCardNumber" placeholder="XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX" required autofocus>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
        	<label for="membershipCSV">Card CSV Code</label>
        	<input type="text" class="form-control" id="membershipCSV" name="membershipCSV" placeholder="XXXX" required>
        </div>
        
        <p>By clicking accept, your membership will be extended by 6 months and will start at the moment the transaction is performed.</p>
        
        <div class="form-group">
      	 	<a class="btn btn-default" href="{{base_url}}/membership">Cancel</a>
        	<button class="btn btn-success" type="submit">Purchase</button>
        </div>
      </form>
		
	</div>
</div>
      